General.Name: Opdenergy Holding SA
General.GicIndustry: Independent Power and Renewable Electricity Producers
General.Description: Opdenergy Holding, S.A., an independent renewable energy producer, engages in the development, construction, operation, and maintenance, production of electricity. It focuses on the solar photovoltaic and onshore wind energy production. The company was incorporated in 2005 and is based in Madrid, Spain.
